{"tid":1630981,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"市民觀星筆照射軍營   外牆解放軍首舉黃旗警告","createTime":"2019-10-06T14:19:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T18:30:54.000Z","uid":66271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"953922d5a51f8a7f31f35fb8925fcd916f1104b3","tid":1630981,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:19:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191006/large/1570365293_94f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191006%2Flarge%2F1570365293_94f7.jpg&h=eb9ed2ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n解放軍首次舉黃旗！ 特首林鄭月娥前日（4日）宣佈引用《緊急法》硬推《蒙面法》，網民發起今日在港島及九龍區遊行，呼籲香港人上街反抗。 至夜晚7時左右，警方在旺角清場，黑衣市民遂經窩打老道退至九龍塘一帶。 當群眾退至九龍塘軍營一帶時，有市民以觀星筆照射其中一棟建築物外牆<br />\n<br />\n其後，有一名身穿迷彩服的駐港解放軍在建築物頂樓舉起黃旗，內容為「你正在違反法例，可能被檢控」。 不過，軍人在舉黃旗後未有其他行動，而市民最後亦無其他衝擊行為。"},{"pid":"7061da431f0dc320b1b8923929a96f4777048210","tid":1630981,"uid":37596,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:20:07.000Z","msg":"班雷射撚真係越來越ON9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c96e9cd9f1012cf572643412de65931652d9a072","tid":1630981,"uid":256019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:22:04.000Z","msg":"真勇士！用laser point射軍營，真係要有對方隨時開槍心理準備，印象中以前有俄佬試過.."},{"pid":"cee7e9da27be321bec591a10dde633c53fd3a189","tid":1630981,"uid":118520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7061da431f0dc320b1b8923929a96f4777048210","tid":1630981,"uid":37596,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:20:07.000Z","msg":"班雷射撚真係越來越ON9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:22:29.000Z","msg":"鬼黎？"},{"pid":"c98e91c3bbf622ddff434bdd6e0fa7144bf6a79f","tid":1630981,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7061da431f0dc320b1b8923929a96f4777048210","tid":1630981,"uid":37596,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"re